    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone prioritizing functionality over aesthetics. The engine and transmission are in good working order, and the car has successfully passed all recent safety inspections, ensuring it is road-ready. However, please be aware of its age; the exterior paint shows some fading and minor scratches, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery and some plastic trim pieces. This is a solid, honest car that performs its primary duties well but exhibits the expected character of a well-used vehicle.",
