      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, naturally aspirated with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive double-VANOS timing system overhaul and structural subframe reinforcement to mitigate floor pan fatigue. The suspension maintains its communicative feedback with upgraded polyurethane bushings, while the braking system remains fade-resistant under spirited load. Though the finish shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain remains thermally efficient and mechanically tight, offering a visceral analog driving experience.",
